summary: Since everyone but me has watched the new Good Omens adaptation, I thought I’d share my favourite fic rec from days of yore (aka...
body:
Since everyone but me has watched the new Good Omens adaptation, I thought I’d share my favourite fic rec from days of yore (aka 2003) : 

Living Arangements by afrai
Summary: Everyone is human, even when they aren’t.
Pairing: Crowley/Aziraphale

Quote from fic:
“His problem was that he’d always had hope. He’d always believes that everything would turn out more or less all right in the end, if only because it had always done so before.”

It’s probably my favourite thing I’ve read in that fandom! Mind the tags.
